result.reason: Trend Micro TMDS blocks outgoing RDP sessions initiated from within an RDP-connected session — this is antivirus policy enforcement unrelated to mRemoteNG; the same behavior occurs with standard mstsc.exe in the same jump-host scenario.
result.approach: Close as external/antivirus issue; advise user to test with mstsc.exe and contact Trend Micro if confirmed not mRemoteNG-specific.
